  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA20-kiḷavi">itu parattaiyiṟ pirintu vanta talaimakaṉ “yāraiyu maṟiyēṉ” eṉṟuk kūṟiyataṟkut talaivi colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what SHE said to HIM who came back from the other woman, saying “I do not know of anybody!”.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA20">
<l>            aiya kuṟumakaṭ kaṇṭikum vaiki</l>
<l>            makiḻnaṉ mārpiṟ ṟuñci yaviḻiṇart </l>
<l>            tēmpāy marāaṅ kamaḻuṅ kūntaṟ</l>
<l>            ṟuḷaṅkiya lacaivarak kaliṅkan tuyalvarac</l>
<l>            ceṟitoṭi teḷirppa vīci maṟukiṟ </l>
<l>            pūppō luṇkaṇ peyarppa nōkkic</l>
<l>            ceṉṟaṉaḷ vāḻiya maṭantai nuṇpal</l>
<l>            cuṇaṅkaṇi yuṟṟa viḷaṅku pūṇaṇ</l>
<l>            mārpuṟu muyakkiṭai ñemirnta cōrkuḻaip</l>
<l>            paḻampiṇi vaikiya tōḷiṇaik </l>
<l>            kuḻainta kōtaik koṭimuyaṅ kalaḷē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lord, we've seen the little woman:</l>
<l>she went – may the girl live –</l>
<l rend="indent">discharging looks from [her] flower-like kajal eyes in</l>
<l rend="indent">the street, flinging [her arms] so that [her] tight bracelets sparkled,</l>
<l rend="indent2">garment coming into swinging, tresses coming into swaying movement,</l>
<l rend="indent2">fragrant of the honey-springing Marāam tree</l>
<l rend="indent3">with opening [flower] clusters,</l>
<l>having slept tightly<note place="foot">Can <term xml:lang="ta">vaiki</term>, in spite of its position, be taken as an adverb to <term xml:lang="ta">tuñci</term>?</note> on the chest of the delightful man.</l>
<l rend="indent3">She of shining ornaments,</l>
<l rend="indent3">[once] adorned with fine [and] many beauty spots,</l>
<l rend="indent4">[her] shoulder pair kept within the old bond, earrings slipped</l>
<l rend="indent4">down, crushed in the middle of an embrace by [his] chest,</l>
<l rend="indent3">is [now] unembraced, a creeper [that has become] a withered garland.</l>
           
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
            </text>
